>?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>59</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Properties","id":"properties_2"},{"text":"Methods","id":"methods"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"O mixin WindowOrWorkerGlobalScope descreve vários recursos comuns às interfaces Window e WorkerGlobalScope. Cada uma dessas interfaces pode, obviamente, adicionar mais recursos além dos listados abaixo.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"WindowBase64","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"WindowOrWorkerGlobalScope","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"WindowOrWorkerGlobalScope","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"WindowBase64","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"WindowOrWorkerGlobalScope","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/windoworworkerglobalscope","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/windoworworkerglobalscope/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{